    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "A new skink of the genus Subdoluseps Freitas, Datta-Roy, Karanth, Grismer & Siler, 2019 (Squamata: Scincidae) from southern Vietnam" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674029>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674031>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674033>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674025>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674035> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674029>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Holotype of Subdoluseps vietnamensis sp. nov., ITBCZ 5842.A, general view, in life (photo by Sang N. Nguyen); B&C, line drawing of lateral and dorsal views of head (drawn by Manh V. Le)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4674029/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674031>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Paratypes of Subdoluseps vietnamensis sp. nov. in life. A, ITBCZ 5843, adult female (photo by Sang N. Nguyen); B, ITBCZ 7038, adult male; C, ITBCZ 7046, adult male; D, ITBCZ 7056, adult female; E, ITBCZ 7059, adult female; F, ITBCZ 7070, juvenile (photos by Manh V. Le)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4674031/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674033>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitats of Subdoluseps vietnamensis sp. nov. from southern Vietnam. A&B, earleaf acacia plantation and dipterocarp forest on the sandy soil in Ho Tram area, Xuyen Moc District, Ba Ria-Vung Tau Province, respectively; C, rubber plantation in La Gi Town, Binh Thuan Province (Photos by Manh V. Le)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4674033/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674025>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map showing the type localities of Subdoluseps vietnamensis sp. nov. (site 5) and S. frontoparietale (site 16) and other examined samples of S. bowringii. Vietnam: 1, Ngu Hanh Son District, Da Nang City; 2, Cu Lao Cham Island, Quang Nam Province; 3, Hon Ba, Khanh Hoa Province; 4, La Gi Town, Binh Thuan Province; 5, Ho Tram, Xuyen Moc District, Ba Ria- Vung Tau Province; 6, Nui Lon Mountain, Ba Ria-Vung Tau Province; 7, Con Dao Island, Ba Ria-Vung Tau Province; 8, Suoi Ngo, Tan Chau District, Tay Ninh Province; 9, Ba Den Mountain, Tay Ninh Province; 10, Lo Go-Xa Mat, Tay Ninh Province; 11, Hon Chong, Kien Giang Province; 12, Nam Du Island, Kien Giang Province; 13, Phu Quoc Island, Kien Giang Province; Cambodia: 14, Phnom Sruoch, Kampong Speu District, Khampong Speu Province; 15, Che Teal Chrum, Pursat Province; Thailand: and 16, Muak Lek District, Saraburi Province." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4674025/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4674035>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Examined specimens of Subdoluseps frontoparietale from its type locality in Thailand.A, Holotype FMNH 178262 (photo by Joshua Mata and Alan Resetar [Field Museum, Chicago, USA]); B, ZMKU R 00705; C, ZMKU R 00706, in life; D, ZMKU R 00707, juvenile (photos by Attapol Rujirawan)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4674035/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

